    "content": "### Overview\r\n**Echo Medi Mental Health Platform** is a modern web application designed to make mental health services more accessible. It allows users to **book therapy sessions**, **take psychological assessments**, and **read curated articles** by mental health professionals. The platform emphasizes simplicity, usability, and local integration to support users on their wellness journey.\r\n\r\n### Key Features\r\n- **Appointment Booking**: Users can browse available time slots, choose a preferred date and time, and book a consultation session with a licensed therapist.\r\n- **Psychological Assessments**: The platform provides self-assessment tools for MBTI, stress, depression, anxiety, and more, with results displayed instantly.\r\n- **Expert Articles**: Users can read insightful, expert-written articles covering mental health, emotional well-being, and personal development strategies.\r\n\r\n### Tech Stack\r\n- **Frontend**: Next.js with the App Router, Tailwind CSS, and Shadcn UI components.\r\n- **Backend**: Strapi CMS, Node.js.\r\n- **Database**: SQLite â€“ lightweight and ideal for rapid development.\r\n- **Security**: OTP-based authentication using FPT SMS Brandname service.\r\n\r\n### Live Demo\r\nðŸ”— [tamly.echomedi.com](https://tamly.echomedi.com/)",
